text: Ayu Bulantrisna Djelantik (8 September 1947 - 24 February 2021) was a Dutch- born Indonesian traditional Balinese dancer. She was an ENT specialist and a lecturer at the faculty of medicine at Padjadjaran University. Bulantrisna died on 24 February 2021 of pancreatic cancer at the age of 73. ==References== Category:1947 births Category:2021 deaths Category:Dancers Category:Deaths from pancreatic cancer Category:Cancer deaths in Indonesia Category:Indonesian people
